  May 6-8, 2020 Fukuoka, Japan
        Construct a Low Carbon SocietyThe10th International Congress on Engineering and Information (ICEAI)will take place from May 6-8, 2020 at Fukuoka, Japan. Aiming to creating a better living environment by mitigating air pollution from industry and transportation, the conference of this year focuses on topics “Low Carbon Society” but not limited to:◆ Low Carbon Technology◆ Environmental Sciences◆ Information and Applied Sciences◆ Earth Sciences◆ Engineering◆ More fields related but not limitedSubmit HERE!Socializing Tour in Kyushu九州ICEAI 2020 brings you to the well-known sightseeing spots to explore the culture and most beautiful scenery in Kyushu. Seasonal limited, Hanoi Fuji Garden has large area of rattan and intoxicating wisteria dome and wisteria tunnel. Surrounded by oceans, Itoshima is famous for its sunset scenery. The couple rock, which is connected by the Shinto ropes, is under the leadership of Sakurai Shrine.If you are interested in these attractions, register and join us!  Important DateMail: info.iceai@iceai.org
